<br />

<br />
My question is this:
<br />

<br />
Where do I start with my research of the class? I have read the FAQ and am starting to read the suggested guides. The bard has a full set of Singing Steel, as well as all the songs for level (level 54).
<br />

<br />
All I have ever played in 3 years of EQ is my cleric main. I have 6 alts, none of which I have ever taken past level 10, since I simply use them for bank space to tradeskill on my main.</span></td>
